Progression Chart

Exercises that build on one another are called progressions, with each exercise requiring more mobility and/or strength than the previous. The progressions below are further sorted by categories of movements that tend to have overlap in muscles used. For a full body exercise try to practice at least one exercise for each category!

For a list of all exercise check out our exercises wiki
